===message:Maybe the colonies might have lived in "harmony" without the Europeans coming over and starting a war.  But, the people living in the colonies all mostly descended from Europe.  I think that the main struggles where because the people of Europe still had the whole Roman Empire motif going.  They thought that the more land would equal more power.  More power leading to more money.  The colonies in America where just caught in the middle of the struggle.  But, the Indians would have been living in harmony if it wasn't for the settlers coming and taking over land.  
